text: Jessica Naz (born 24 September 2000) is an English footballer who plays as a Forward for FA Women's Super League club Tottenham Hotspur. ==Club career== On 23 February 2018, Naz made her debut for Arsenal. She substituted in for Heather O'Reilly for the last three minutes of Arsenal's 1–0 win over Everton in the 2017–18 season. ==References== ==External links== * *Profile at Tottenham Hotspur F.C.
